                        <interp inst="t18540814-906-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">The prisoner was further charged with having been before convicted.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18540814-name-189" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18540814-name-189" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18540814-name-189" type="surname" value="GUIVER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18540814-name-189" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN GUIVER</persName>
                  </hi>. I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Central Criminal Court; William George, convicted June</hi>, 1838, <hi rend="italic">of stealing half a bushed of oats; confined two days</hi>)—I was present—the prisoner is the man.</p>
               <p>
